# 1. Ignore everything by default
*

# 2. Allow directories so we can see files inside them
!*/

# 3. Explicitly allow the files you want to keep
!*.c
!*.h
!*.txt
!README.md
!.gitignore

# 4. Specifically ignore macOS system files (even if allowed above)
**/.DS_Store
.DS_Store?

# 5. Specifically ignore object files and compiled binaries
*.o
*.obj
*.out
